node.text:
- Mother and Child - 
.
This is a surrealistic blend between digital sculpture and oddly satisfying animation, with the repetitive motion as the heart and soul. The layered sculpture symbolises the nature of human personalities; on the outside smooth, whole and simple but inside layer upon layer, complex and deep.
.
Available on @superrare.co today 💎
.
.
#wannerstedt #layers #mother #loop #2021 #3d #3dart #animation #satisfying #nft #cryptoart #artdirection
